# Catch-all: maintainers see every PR by default. Path-specific lines
# below either narrow or widen the reviewer set.
*                              @trendvidia/maintainers

# --- Wire format (every change rebroadcasts to all 9 ports) ---------------
# Touching anything here is a cross-port event. Maintainer review is required.
/proto/                        @trendvidia/maintainers
/docs/grammar.ebnf             @trendvidia/maintainers
/docs/grammar.svg              @trendvidia/maintainers
/docs/draft-*.txt              @trendvidia/maintainers
/docs/HARDENING.md             @trendvidia/maintainers
/testdata/                     @trendvidia/maintainers
/governance.pxf                @trendvidia/maintainers
/STABILITY.md                  @trendvidia/maintainers
/SECURITY.md                   @trendvidia/maintainers
/GOVERNANCE.md                 @trendvidia/maintainers

# --- Tooling and editors (looser — open to broader reviewer pool) --------
/cmd/                          @trendvidia/contributors @trendvidia/maintainers
/scripts/                      @trendvidia/contributors @trendvidia/maintainers
/editors/                      @trendvidia/contributors @trendvidia/maintainers

# --- CI / repo plumbing (maintainer review keeps supply chain trustworthy) -
/.github/                      @trendvidia/maintainers
/go.mod                        @trendvidia/maintainers
/go.sum                        @trendvidia/maintainers

